FBIS4-39609 "drsov111_a_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-111 Daily Report 8 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin To Bypass Parliament in Deployment Yeltsin To Bypass Parliament in Deployment LD0806191494 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network in Georgian 1000 GMT 8 Jun 94 LD0806191494 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network Georgian BFN [Text] Georgian Information Agency correspondent Besik Pipia has reported from St. Petersburg, quoting reliable sources, that Boris Yeltsin is to sign a decree authorizing the introduction of peacekeeping forces to the zone of the Georgian-Abkhaz conflict. According to the above-mentioned sources, the peacekeeping forces will not wait for the decree to be approved by the Russian parliament before they embark on their peace mission.
